race.comment: BENTLEY HARRIS (8) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on his speedy win the start prior, getting around Q Straight over 300m in 16.62. Hot win two back and looks the one to beat here. MISS RICO (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (17.66) in a NG at Taree Super Track. Has a good record here including five wins. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings eight times from 13 attempts. Warrants plenty of respect. WALK ME DADDY (3) produced a moderate effort last time when fifth at this track over 411m behind Integrity Al (24.29) in a Grade 5. Key runner on best form. WHY A MACIE (7) is worth including.
